### CCR-025 — Overlay Color Override
###
### 검증:
### - Table 별 overlay_colors PATCH
### - CC + Overlay 동일 override 수신

@host = http://localhost:8000
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 42.1 GET /tables/{id} — 현재 색상 설정
GET {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: { ..., overlayColors: {...} }, error }

### 42.2 PUT /tables/{id} — overlay_colors override
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "overlayColors": {
    "badgeCheck": "#00FF88",
    "badgeFold": "#888888"
  }
}

# 예상: 200 + envelope { data: TableOut, error: null }
# WS /ws/overlay 수신 검증은 별도 (HTTP 범위 밖)
